column2: SELECT U.up_id, S.* FROM #upLoad U CROSS APPLY (SELECT Objid FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (U.up_ra , U.up_dec , U.up_sep) ) S SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camCol, p.field, p.obj, cast (str (p.ra, #, #) as float) as ra, cast (str (p.[dec], #, #) as float) as dec, p.r FROM ..Star AS p JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id WHERE p.psfMag_r < # ORDER BY x.up_id
